<![CDATA[<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400"><tbody><tr valign="top" height="400"><td teditid="c1r1" aeditid="c1r1" locked="0" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Fellow_Application__c.Applicant_First_Name__c},<br><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">We are pleased to inform you that you are under consideration for the Climate Corps fellowship – congratulations on successfully completing the first step in the fellow selection process!&nbsp; &nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Please watch for a scheduling email from climatecorps@cet.net.cn in about 1-3 working days to schedule an interview. Please note that scheduling emails will be sent from climatecorps@cet.net.cn. It is advisable to add this email address to your list of safe senders. Please respond to the scheduling email as soon as possible and if you have scheduling conflicts, are traveling, etc. please communicate your availability to climatecorps@cet.net.cn as soon as possible.&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Be advised that scheduling emails will include time options for you to select as well as a link to connect on Zoom video. For your interview, try to find a quiet place with a strong internet connection.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"><font face="Verdana, 